dct_description_sm: Relief shown by 25 meter contour interval, spot heights, and shading. Prime meridian: Paris. "Graticulate lines of this sheet are in Grades East of Paris." are in purple Reproduced by the U.S. Army Map Service. Most maps are facsimiles, (grids were added?) See index. Geographic coverage complete in 92 sheets. Each sheet individually titled.
